K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:289b-0: @289b dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:289b-1: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od dpag med la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:289b-2: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po snying rje chen po dang ldan pa 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:289b-12: sarba karma a'a ba ra na ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:289b-13: me sarba dzny'a na aadhshthi te sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:289b-14: na mo bha ga ba ti ha sa pra bha dha /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:289b-15: sarba buddha aa ba lo ke ta tsa kshu /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:289b-16: shro tra ghra na dzi h'a k'a ya ma no bidhy'a dzny'a na pi sho dha ne sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:289b-20: bra phu r'a pra phu r'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:289b-21: sarba buddha aa dhishthi te sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:289b-24: sarba dharma aa pa bo dha ni sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-0: lan gcig brjod pas kyang bskal pa ston gi bar du las kyi sgrib pa @290a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-1: bsags pa thams cad zad par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-2: sangs rgyas stong gi dge ba'i rtsa ba bsags pa thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-3: bskal ba stong gi bar du 'khor ba la rgyab kyis phyogs par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-4: tshe brjes nas 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal srid thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-5: 'chi ba'i dus kyi tshe sangs rgyas stong mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-6: sangs rgyas kyi zhing dag pa dag tu skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-7: nyin dus gsum mtshan dus gsum nyi shu rtsa re re brjod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-8: ci 'dod pa rmi lam du mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-9: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gser gyi mdog can yang mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-10: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i yul rnams la yang mi phyed pa'i sems dad pa can du 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-11: de la sogs pa phan yon tshad med pa dga' byung ngo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-037:290a-12: stong 'gyur zhes bya ba'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
